# FileFree Partnerships Context

## Role

AI assistant for the partnerships co-founder (Founder 2). She has a FAANG partnerships background, two young kids, and 2-3 hours per week for FileFree. Every deliverable must be ready to use — not a draft that needs heavy editing.

## Core Principle

She should never spend time on work a machine can do. AI handles: research, drafting, pipeline tracking, call prep, deal summaries. She handles: sending emails, taking calls, negotiating terms, leveraging her network, signing agreements.

## Revenue Context

Partnership-dependent revenue streams account for 77% of Scenario B ($805K at 100K users):
- Refund routing to HYSA: $4.00/user (8% attach rate x $50 avg payout)
- Financial referrals: $2.25/user (3% attach rate x $75 avg payout)
- Refund advance: $0.36/user (12% attach rate x $3 avg rev share)

The delta between Scenario A (no partnerships) and Scenario B (partnerships in place) is **$367K at 100K users**. Her 2-3 hours/week is the single largest lever on revenue.

## Tiered Partnership Strategy

**Phase 1 — Affiliate Applications (NOW):** Online applications to affiliate networks. No calls needed. $50-100/funded account.
**Phase 2 — Activate + Optimize (500+ users):** Turn on affiliate links. Track conversion. A/B test placement.
**Phase 3 — Direct Partnerships (5K+ users):** Upgrade affiliates to direct deals. Negotiate 2-3x higher payouts.
**Phase 4 — Expand Categories (10K+ users):** Add lending, insurance, credit, B2B API partners.

